	(text "Notes\n1. Temp Sensor connected to VINP Plane will cause it to burn up and damage U4 and U7. DNP\n2. Fault LED works in all conditions except reverse polarity. Faults cut power to the board.\n3. Input range 5V-24V, Maximum No Damage Input Range ±33V.\n   TVS will adsorb higher transients. See JMBJ33CA datasheet.\n4. Q3-Q4 installed, nominal current 5A, Short Circuit Current 10A.\n   Q1-Q4 installed, nominal current 10A, Short Circuit Current 20A.\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
